snippet.title: Amber Heard’s Neighbor EXPOSES James Franco AFFAIR! | her lawyers CAUGHT in a MAJOR LIE! #shorts
snippet.description:
As week 3 of the Johnny Depp vs Amber Heard defamation trial wraps up, Amber's former neighbor Ami Goodhart did an exclusive interview on the popcorned planet YouTube channel, in which she divulged some pretty important details of the James Franco and Amber Heard elevator encounter at the Eastern Columbia Building, in which Ami still resides and has lived in even before Johnny and Amber moved in. 

#JohnnyDepp #AmberHeard #DeppVsHeard
